ts portfolio of services comprises on-site coordination and program management, rental furniture and furnishings, exhibit design and construction. It provides logistics and shipping services, installation and dismantling services, refurbishing of exhibits and material handling. The company offers marketing services in the US, France, Germany, the UK and the UAE, and travel and recreation services in the US and Canada. Viad is headquartered in Phoenix, Arizona, the US.
								

