Home»Business Groups»GES
        











Visit GES.com
GES, a global full-service provider for live events, partners with show organizers, exhibitors and brand marketers to create high-value, face-to-face events. We offer a complete range of services, from the design and production of compelling, immersive experiences that engage audiences and build brand awareness, to material handling, rigging, electrical and other on-site services. In addition, GES offers clients a full suite of audio-visual services from creative and technology to content and design along with online tools powered by next generation technologies that help them easily manage the complexities of their events.

Exhibitions
Conferences
Corporate Events
Consumer Events



The Markets we Serve
The Live Events industry is a large market and GES serves all major segments with a dominant position in Exhibitions. We are pursuing a focused and disciplined growth strategy, with the goal of expanding our share in the currently under-penetrated Corporate Event and Conference segments. These segments offer strong growth opportunity with a higher margin profile than Exhibitions, which will help to improve profitability and diversify our revenue mix over the long-term.





Exhibitions
The primary purpose is to facilitate B2B & B2C sales/marketing.  Host and exhibitors typically pay for services.










Conferences
The primary purpose is to facilitate attendee education; expo or trade show may be held in conjunction to further facilitate attendee education. Host and exhibitors typically pay for services.














Corporate Events
The primary purpose is to facilitate attendee education of sponsoring company’s products or product ecosystem. Corporation or host pays for services.









Consumer Events
The primary purpose is to entertain, educate or create an experience, typically around a specific genre.






















GES offers a comprehensive and award-winning range of services and innovative technology, including creative design, strategy, audio visual, show production and event accommodations to help our clients maximize performance and achieve their visions through face-to-face experiences. In connection with our focused growth strategy, we have made important acquisitions of leading Audio-Visual (AV) production and Event Technology firms. These new services are a perfect complement to our Core Services. They also have higher-margins and provide a more compelling offering to penetrate Corporate Events and Conferences where AV is larger portion of the total spend. 

Core Services
Event Technology
Audio-Visual








Core Services
GES has over 80 years of experience delivering epic live event experiences that maximize impact, spark the imagination and inspire – from creating the largest trade shows and powerful corporate events to carefully crafting small but meaningful exhibits, we are your experts.



Event Planning & Production
Logistics (electrical, rigging, carpet, install, dismantle, shipping, storing and anything in between)




Furnishings & Graphics
Creative Services
Strategy & Marketing Services
Agency Services




Measurement Services
Exhibit Program Management
Custom Design & Fabrication
Rental Exhibits






Event Technology
GES is constantly investing in new, innovative technology to make our clients’ jobs easier and their events better. Recent acquisitions include a leading provider of end-to-end event accommodations solutions and an industry leading and highly-scalable registration and data analytics platform.

Event Management Tools 

Online Ordering Capabilities 
Sponsorship Management tools 
