Audio-Visual
GES’ AV team delivers high-impact multi-media services and technology across the live event spectrum with significant opportunity for high-margin growth. We combine the science of innovative digital solutions with the latest in audio visual technology and superior service to create award-winning attendee engagements.

Video Projection
